 Prophet slept through his night prayer or he was ill, he would pray twelve cycles in the day. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 746\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33619,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/sunan-maghrib-if-you-wish\/","url_meta":{"origin":1941,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recommended two raka&#8217;at before Maghrib","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Muzanni reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPray before the sunset prayer.\u201d The Prophet said on the third time, \u201cFor whomever wishes,\u201d as he disliked for people to consider it an obligatory tradition. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1183 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7927,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/11\/salah-as-you-see-me-praying\/","url_meta":{"origin":1941,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Pray as you see the Prophet praying","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn al-Huwayrith reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Pray as you have seen me praying. When the time for prayer arrives, let one of you announce the call to prayer for everyone and then let the older of you lead the prayer.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1941","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1941"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1941\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1941"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1941"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1941"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}